    <div class="span9" id="main-content" style="background-color:white!important"><br>
        <h1 id="title-heading">Research Areas</h1>
        <ul><li><a href="#algebra-and-number-theory">Algebra and Number Theory</a></li><li><a href="#analysis--differential-geometry">Analysis & Differential Geometry</a></li><li><a href="#biomedical-informatics">Biomedical Informatics</a></li><li><a href="#center-for-language-and-information-research-clir">Center for Language and Information Research (CLIR)</a></li><li><a href="#data-and-networked-systems">Data and Networked Systems</a></li><li><a href="#data-mining-and-machine-learning">Data Mining and Machine Learning</a></li><li><a href="#databases-and-information-management">Databases and Information Management</a></li><li><a href="#discrete-mathematics--theoretical-computer-science">Discrete Mathematics & Theoretical Computer Science</a></li><li><a href="#distributed-computing-laboratory">Distributed Computing Laboratory</a></li><li><a href="#imaging-informatics">Imaging Informatics</a></li><li><a href="#numerical-analysis--scientific-computing">Numerical Analysis & Scientific Computing</a></li></ul><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="algebra-and-number-theory"></a><h2>Algebra and Number Theory</h2></div><div class="group-description">Algebra, Algebraic Groups, Algebraic Geometry, Analytic Number Theory, Arithmetic Geometry, Moonshine, Modular forms, Vertex Algebra</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="https://sites.google.com/site/emoryalgebraseminarschedule/home">https://sites.google.com/site/emoryalgebraseminarschedule/home</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=John-Duncan">John Duncan</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ken-Ono">Ken Ono</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Raman-Parimala">Raman Parimala</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Victoria-Powers">Victoria Powers</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Suresh-Venapally">Suresh Venapally</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=David-Zureick-Brown">David Zureick-Brown</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="analysis--differential-geometry"></a><h2>Analysis & Differential Geometry</h2></div><div class="group-description">Differential geometry, applied analysis, partial differential equations, complex analysis, geometric function theory, spectral theory, and mathematical physics.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href=""></a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=David-Borthwick">David Borthwick</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Vladimir-Oliker">Vladimir Oliker</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Shanshuang-Yang">Shanshuang Yang</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="biomedical-informatics"></a><h2>Biomedical Informatics</h2></div><div class="group-description">Biomedical informatics leverages virtually all areas of biomedical, computational, physical and social science. Research groups include cancer,  clinical phenotyping, mHealth, healthcare analytics, human genetics, high-throughput drug discovery, infectious diseases, neurosciences, pathology, radiology and real-time streaming health analytics, among others.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://bmi.emory.edu">http://bmi.emory.edu</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Gari-Clifford">Gari Clifford</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Lee-Cooper">Lee Cooper</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Joyce-Ho">Joyce Ho</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Jun-Kong">Jun Kong</a>, <a href="http://www.bmi.emory.edu/Li">Qiao Li</a>, <a href="http://www.bmi.emory.edu/QLong">Qi Long</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Shamim-Nemati">Shamim Nemati</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Andrew-Post">Andrew Post</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Zhaohui-Steve-Qin">Zhaohui "Steve" Qin</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ashish-Sharma">Ashish Sharma</a>, <a href="http://www.bmi.emory.edu/yansun">Yan Sun</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Li-Xiong">Li Xiong</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="center-for-language-and-information-research-clir"></a><h2>Center for Language and Information Research (CLIR)</h2></div><div class="group-description">We study computational linguistics, and develop new techniques for natural language processing, information retrieval and web search and text mining.<br>
<b>Related Links:</b>
<br><a href="http://psychology.emory.edu/cognition/wolff/main2.html">Mind & Language Lab</a><br>
<a href="http://ir.mathcs.emory.edu/">IR Lab</a></div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://clir.emory.edu/">http://clir.emory.edu/</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Eugene-Agichtein">Eugene Agichtein</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Jinho-Choi">Jinho Choi</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Davide-Fossati">Davide Fossati</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Andrew-Post">Andrew Post</a>, <a href="http://psychology.emory.edu/cognition/wolff/main2.html">Phillip Wolf</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="data-and-networked-systems"></a><h2>Data and Networked Systems</h2></div><div class="group-description">We research how to build and improve scalable distributed systems, databases and networking to support the collection, analysis and understanding of large volumes of data.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://www.ymsir.com/projects.html">http://www.ymsir.com/projects.html</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Shun-Yan-Cheung">Shun Yan Cheung</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ken-Mandelberg">Ken Mandelberg</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Vaidy-Sunderam">Vaidy Sunderam</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ymir-Vigfusson">Ymir Vigfusson</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Avani-Wildani">Avani Wildani</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="data-mining-and-machine-learning"></a><h2>Data Mining and Machine Learning</h2></div><div class="group-description">We study algorithms and methods for finding patterns and insights in data to build more intelligent and effective systems.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/Research/Area/datainfo/">http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/Research/Area/datainfo/</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Eugene-Agichtein">Eugene Agichtein</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Jinho-Choi">Jinho Choi</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Gari-Clifford">Gari Clifford</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Lee-Cooper">Lee Cooper</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Joyce-Ho">Joyce Ho</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Shamim-Nemati">Shamim Nemati</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Zhaohui-Steve-Qin">Zhaohui "Steve" Qin</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ymir-Vigfusson">Ymir Vigfusson</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Avani-Wildani">Avani Wildani</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Li-Xiong">Li Xiong</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="databases-and-information-management"></a><h2>Databases and Information Management</h2></div><div class="group-description">We work on storage, organization, management and retrieval of medical, public health, web and biological data.<br>
<b>Related Links:</b>
<br><a href="http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/aims/">AIMS Lab</a><br>
<a href="http://ir.mathcs.emory.edu/">IR Lab</a></div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/Research/Area/datainfo/">http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/Research/Area/datainfo/</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Eugene-Agichtein">Eugene Agichtein</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Shun-Yan-Cheung">Shun Yan Cheung</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=James-Lu">James Lu</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ymir-Vigfusson">Ymir Vigfusson</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Avani-Wildani">Avani Wildani</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Li-Xiong">Li Xiong</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="discrete-mathematics--theoretical-computer-science"></a><h2>Discrete Mathematics & Theoretical Computer Science</h2></div><div class="group-description">Ordered combinatorial and algebraic structures, theory of computation, circuit complexity, geometric algorithms, approximation algorithms, graph theory, hypergraphs, ramsey theory, combinatorics, extremal graph theory, approximation algorithms, combinatorial optimization, polyhedral combinatorics, mathematical programming, combinatorial scientific computing.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/~rg/dmtcs.html">http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/~rg/dmtcs.html</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Dwight-Duffus">Dwight Duffus</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ron-Gould">Ron Gould</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Michelangelo-Grigni">Michelangelo Grigni</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Hao-Huang">Hao Huang</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Vojtech-Rodl">Vojtech Rodl</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Robert-Roth">Robert Roth</a>, <a href="http://www.staff.amu.edu.pl/~rucinski/">Andrzej Rucinski</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="distributed-computing-laboratory"></a><h2>Distributed Computing Laboratory</h2></div><div class="group-description">Metacomputing, distributed systems, collaboration technologies, and networking. Current projects are focusing on self-organizing frameworks for cooperative resource-sharing and collaboration group communication in the context of peer-to-peer networks.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://cls.emory.edu/">http://cls.emory.edu/</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Vaidy-Sunderam">Vaidy Sunderam</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="imaging-informatics"></a><h2>Imaging Informatics</h2></div><div class="group-description">Development of methods for labeling anatomic and micro-anatomic structures found in images, systems software and techniques for management and analysis of very large image data, and techniques and software tools for sharing this labeling information in a computational grid architecture.

Computational methods for large-scale image processing, in particular, image deblurring, image reconstruction, image registration.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://www.bmi.emory.edu/">http://www.bmi.emory.edu/</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Lee-Cooper">Lee Cooper</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Jun-Kong">Jun Kong</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=James-Nagy">James Nagy</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Lars-Ruthotto">Lars Ruthotto</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Ashish-Sharma">Ashish Sharma</a></div><hr><div class="group-name"><a name="numerical-analysis--scientific-computing"></a><h2>Numerical Analysis & Scientific Computing</h2></div><div class="group-description">Numerical Linear Algebra, Numerical Optimization, Numerical Partial Differential Equations, Numerical Methods for Inverse Problems, Image Processing, Geophysics, Computational Fluid Dynamics, Numerical Methods for Complex Networks, Parallel and Distributed Computing.</div><div class="group-website-label"><h4>Website:</h4></div><div class="group-website"><a href="http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/Research/Area/ScientificComputing/">http://www.mathcs.emory.edu/Research/Area/ScientificComputing/</a></div><div class="group-people-label"><h4>People:</h4></div><div class="group-people-list"><a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Michele-Benzi">Michele Benzi</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=James-Nagy">James Nagy</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Lars-Ruthotto">Lars Ruthotto</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Vaidy-Sunderam">Vaidy Sunderam</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Alessandro-Veneziani">Alessandro Veneziani</a>, <a href="../../people/faculty/individual.php?NAME=Yuanzhe-Xi">Yuanzhe Xi</a></div><hr>                 

